install
=======
install vagrant rpm https://dl.bintray.com/mitchellh/vagrant/vagrant_1.4.3_x86_64.rpm

install vagrant plugins:

vagrant plugin install vagrant-omnibus
vagrant plugin install vagrant-berkshelf

add vagrant box:

vagrant box add precise64 http://files.vagrantup.com/precise64.box

cd rails3_development_vagrant_machine
bundle install
vagrant up
vagrant ssh

